This directory is populated locally — its contents are not committed.

`mise run setup` (scripts/setup.sh) downloads the ghostty resources from the
thdxg/ghostty release and extracts them here, mirroring a real Ghostty.app
layout:

    Macterm/Resources/
      ghostty/{themes,shell-integration}   ← GHOSTTY_RESOURCES_DIR points at ghostty/
      terminfo/                            ← sibling of ghostty/ (libghostty derives TERMINFO from it)

Everything but this .gitkeep is gitignored. If the app can't find its terminfo
or shell integration, run `mise run setup` to (re)populate this directory.
